OL,3,CPineapple-sized chunk of hail falling
OL,4,Cfrom sky in Texas could break state
OL,5,Crecord
OL,7,FA likely record-breaking hailstone the
OL,8,Fsize of a pineapple has been found in
OL,9,Fnorthern Texas, after a major
OL,10,Fthunderstorm.
OL,12,FThe seven-inch piece of was discovered
OL,13,Fby veteran storm chasers Val and Amy
OL,14,FCastor on the side of the road on
OL,15,FSunday.
OL,17,F"That's the biggest hail I've ever
OL,18,Fseen, and I've been chasing for more
OL,19,Fthan 30 years," said Val Castor.
