OL,7,FHis car was hit by several hail stones
OL,8,Fthe size of baseballs, including one
OL,9,Fthat cracked his windscreen.
OL,11,FThe large piece was visible in a
OL,12,Froadside ditch from almost a hundred
OL,13,Fmetres away, he said.
OL,15,FThe huge hailstone is believed to have
OL,16,Fbroken Texas state records, larger
OL,17,Fthan a 6.4 inch piece which rained
OL,18,Ffrom the sky in 2021 - but it first
OL,19,Fneeds to be verified by a group of
OL,20,Fresearchers.
