OL,7,FHailstones are balls or pieces of ice
OL,8,Fwhich form in clouds, when droplets of
OL,9,Fwater freeze. Large thunderclouds can
OL,10,Fkeep hailstones for a long time, so
OL,11,Fthey grow in size as they become
OL,12,Fcoated with more and more ice.
OL,14,FIn 2023, over 100 people were injured
OL,15,Fin northern Italy after tennis-sized
OL,16,Fhailstones
OL,18,FOne Direction star Louis Tomlinson had
OL,19,Fa cancel a concert in June 2023 after
OL,20,F90 fans in a hailstorm in Colorado.
